Uwera Sarah yavutse ku itariki 1 Kamena 1996

Ni Umunyarwandakazi ukinira ikipe y'Igihugu mu umukino wa kiriketi (criket). ikindi ni umuyobozi wa abakinnyi(captain) bakina hamwe nawe mu Ikipe y'igihugu ya kiriketi (criket) yo mu [[Rwanda|Rwanda.]]<ref>https://www.espncricinfo.com/player/sarah-uwera-1172640/bowling-batting-stats</ref>

Uwera Sarah mu mwaka 2012 nibwo yatangiye gukina kiriketi (criket) akina mu ikipe y'igihugu cy'uRwanda yabatarengeje imyaka 19.<ref>https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Sarah_Uwera</ref>

== Ibyo yakoze ==
Mu ukwezi 1 mu mwaka 2019 nibwo yamenyekanye cyane mu ikipe y'igihugu yu Rwanda bwambere Women's Twenty20 International (WT20I) m'umukino baribukine ni ikipe ya Nigeriya (Nigeria),Uwera yabafashije munsinzi ya Women's Twenty20 International (WT20I) m'umukino wari wabahuje ni ikipe ya Nigeriya (Nigeria) muri sitade y'igihugu cya Nigeriya ihererye Abuja.<ref>https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Sarah_Uwera</ref> mu umwezi kwa Gicurasi 2019 Uwera yakomeje gukuza izina mu irushanwa ryiswe  2019 ICC Women's Qualifier Africa ni amarushanwa yaberaga mugihugu cya Zimbabwe,mu Ukwakira 2019 Uwera nibwo yiswe umuyobozi w'Abakinnyi (captain) kuba bari barabashije gukura ikirenge mumukino bakinnye na Nigeriya.<ref>https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Sarah_Uwera</ref>Muri Gicurasi 2021  Uwera Sarah yongeye nanone kwigaragaza nkumuyobozi w'Abakinnyi mu ikipe y'Igihugu mumarushanwa yiswe 2021 Kwibuka Women's T20 Tournament yabereye mu Rwanda.<ref>https://www.espncricinfo.com/player/sarah-uwera-1172640</ref>

